I'm interested in the god armor could u make the god armor for 2 members of Panthero's Catz. 
  Starcasm6@... wrote: OOC:  if anyone's interested, i've got a god armor for anyone's char, if you want to use it. I'm trying to set g&g up as the wheeljacks of the team 

ghost and goth are busily working away in goth's quarters, which the duo have converted into a makeshift science lab. they are working on seperate peices of something that looks to bo quite large. 
Ghost: alright, you ready to lug this thing outside? 
goth: yeah. hey, we don't have an alternate form for this thing! it's just gotta have an alt mode! 
ghost: ya think? 
goth: yeah! all god armors have one! 
ghost: alright, if you say so... 
      The two begin attaching limbs, as a crowd of bots begins to form. 
ghost: Initiate dna scan! 
      a flood of yellow light erupts from the large quadrupedal machine. it searches for acceptable forms. It finds a male bull elephant. 
goth: alright kids, scramble! 
                        "BONEBREAKER: TRAAANSFORM!" 
      ghost and goth stand back watch as the huge elephant transforms into a slightly more huge mech suit.
